{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he only gave one job, and it's doing lapels in the inside with the lining in there and making stitches and all that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, uh, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Thats's-- that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't get paid for it either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were-- they were, uh-- there was always a Jewish organization that took care of certain expenses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was it, because we had no money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no money-- none, literally no money, what's-- period.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jewelers, whatever jewelry-- which wouldn't have lasted anyhow-- that my mother had was taken away from her, or given away by her when we crossed the border to the smugglers, and so that was it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister certainly couldn't send any money from England, because she-- I think she made a pound a month or something like that, uh, plus room and board, so.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We weren't th-- look, I was never hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However my father did it, he provided food for the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have geese, and we didn't have chicken, and didn't have steak, uh, but whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I made a lot of friends down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Uh, you know, I ate in other homes of boys that were Jewish that were from Belgium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I used to be invited for-- for dinner, which was fabulous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I loved it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, nothing, not very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to wear stars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to wear stars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, that's what got me into trouble when I was arrested and sent to Malines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in a-- in a  movie house with a girl and, uh, you know, didn't wear my star.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My paper said that I was Jewish, and, uh, that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, uh--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
